    "description": "欢迎加入我们的玩家社群和QQ官方群，请告诉我们对这款游戏的想法和意见。<br>《共鸣》玩家QQ群：103224246<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/27d9d90ff63cd021258bb999f072094e.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=108 /></span><br><strong>在这款游戏中，你将遇到多位具有独特演奏和战斗风格的英雄，每位都拥有他们特色的音乐和战斗风格。你还将与十多位不同能力的音乐家一同作战，他们使用的不仅仅是音乐，还有他们独特的战斗技巧。此外，游戏中还有上百种效果各异的道具供你选择和使用，你可以通过巧妙的搭配，创造出千变万化的战斗组合。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/022d93d3115dd1df4481bcbb3dd8a00f.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/0d2504ae67252e0c46aaec0b85946696.poster.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/0d2504ae67252e0c46aaec0b85946696.webm?t=1726296035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/0d2504ae67252e0c46aaec0b85946696.mp4?t=1726296035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>不同的英雄会带来不同的音乐和不同的节奏<br>针对不同的节奏操作，释放出的技能也将完全不同</strong>、<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/bce1200e09c78eb467fe4c948bc62e9a.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/51c7f8d3703b7b2f31f79baac52bec87.poster.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/51c7f8d3703b7b2f31f79baac52bec87.webm?t=1726296035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/51c7f8d3703b7b2f31f79baac52bec87.mp4?t=1726296035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>招募使用不同乐器的音乐家：贝斯手谭佩、吉他手富力吉安、提琴演奏家艾欧莉安等等<br>加入其对应的演奏音色,组成不同的乐队，丰富演奏中的乐曲<br>欣赏不同演奏味道的音乐，感受不同的战斗风格</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/a17a2e154d8745d69dfba9e502b65be0.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/72ae8746fa18c024c4c7c426c3b63785.poster.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/72ae8746fa18c024c4c7c426c3b63785.webm?t=1726296035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/72ae8746fa18c024c4c7c426c3b63785.mp4?t=1726296035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/3cbc708ac5177f04980330cf1a0b8a24.avif?t=1726296035\" width=618 height=184 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/e0d008fd534c9948a4a35dd88d3a8603.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097330/extras/5cb86881c3151faafde8daa74355bece.poster.avif?t=1726296035\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/30973